room_title: Escape room "Raising Atlantis" by PanIQ Escape Room San Jose in San Jose
room_address: 2270 B Quimby Rd, San Jose, CA 95122
room_description: A bizarre geological phenomenon has actually raised a section of the lost city of Atlantis from the depths of the sea. Can your team of archeologists gain access to the ruins and find its treasure before the city disappears once more?
